      "rationale": "All 11 constructs tested at the single ASTM F1717 standard condition (10 mm axial offset, 25 mm/min crosshead rate). A second load-offset condition was planned but not executed due to specimen availability constraints. This factor is below the required level; the shortfall is acknowledged and accepted given that the standard condition is the regulatory submission condition."
