      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric; percentage difference < 10% for all three QoIs.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.41), yield force (0.44), and force at 40 mm (0.42). All values well within ±1.96. Percentage differences 2.0%, 2.1%, and 1.9% respectively. Graphical overlay of force-displacement curves for all 11 constructs confirms shape fidelity beyond the scalar QoIs."
